text: Hum ney bani israeel ko darya say paar ker diya phir unn kay peechay peechay firaon apney lashkar kay sath zulm aur ziyadti kay iraday say chala yahan tak kay jab dobney laga to kehney laga mein eman lata hun kay jiss per bani israeel eman laye hain uss kay siwa koi mabood nahi aur mein musalman mein say hun
